						" ><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw swp_pinterest_icon"></i><span class="swp_share">Pin</span></span></span><span class="swp_count">89</span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_facebook" data-network="facebook"><a class="nc_tweet swp_share_link" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspainonafork.com%2Fspanish-sangria-recipe%2F" data-link="https://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspainonafork.com%2Fspanish-sangria-recipe%2F"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw swp_facebook_icon"></i><span class="swp_share">Share</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button swp_twitter" data-network="twitter"><a class="nc_tweet swp_share_link" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Homemade+Spanish+Sangria+Recipe&url=https%3A%2F%2Fspainonafork.com%2Fspanish-sangria-recipe%2F&via=SpainOnAFork" data-link="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Homemade+Spanish+Sangria+Recipe&url=https%3A%2F%2Fspainonafork.com%2Fspanish-sangria-recipe%2F&via=SpainOnAFork"><span class="swp_count swp_hide"><span class="iconFiller"><span class="spaceManWilly"><i class="sw swp_twitter_icon"></i><span class="swp_share">Tweet</span></span></span></span></a></div><div class="nc_tweetContainer swp_share_button total_shares total_sharesalt" ><span class="swp_count ">89 <span class="swp_label">Shares</span></span></div></div><p>As we all know, nothing says Spain like a cold pitcher of sangria, it is the essence of Spanish culture, well, for a larger amount of the country, certain places like Cantabria or Galicia (among others) prefer a cold cider. This homemade Spanish sangria recipe is about as authentic as it gets.</p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7046" src="https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangria3-22.png?resize=531%2C800&#038;ssl=1" alt="Homemade Spanish Sangria Recipe" width="531" height="800" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangria3-22.png?w=531&amp;ssl=1 531w, https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangria3-22.png?resize=199%2C300&amp;ssl=1 199w, https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangria3-22.png?resize=398%2C600&amp;ssl=1 398w" sizes="(max-width: 531px) 100vw, 531px" /><br />
I have played around with many different ingredients on this one, but this recipe is the one I have used for several years. Sipping on this sangria always reminds me of the summer days, sitting on the patio enjoying good times with friends and family, and always having a couple of pitchers in the fridge to keep the party going.</p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7047" src="https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangria2-33.png?resize=531%2C800&#038;ssl=1" alt="Homemade Spanish Sangria Recipe" width="531" height="800" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangria2-33.png?w=531&amp;ssl=1 531w, https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangria2-33.png?resize=199%2C300&amp;ssl=1 199w, https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangria2-33.png?resize=398%2C600&amp;ssl=1 398w" sizes="(max-width: 531px) 100vw, 531px" /><br />
So, If your searching for the perfect party cocktail that is refreshing, fruity and has a bold flavor, sangria is the drink you´ve been looking for. Watch the video below on how to make this homemade Spanish sangria recipe or print out the recipe card below, and be prepared to create the perfect cocktail for friends and family. Salud!</p>
<p><img data-recalc-dims="1" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-7048" src="https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangriaHOR-44.png?resize=531%2C800&#038;ssl=1" alt="Homemade Spanish Sangria Recipe" width="531" height="800" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangriaHOR-44.png?w=531&amp;ssl=1 531w, https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangriaHOR-44.png?resize=199%2C300&amp;ssl=1 199w, https://i0.wp.com/spainonafork.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/sangriaHOR-44.png?resize=398%2C600&amp;ssl=1 398w" sizes="(max-width: 531px) 100vw, 531px" /></p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Watch the Video Below on How to Make Homemade Spanish Sangria</h3>
